        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[About]]></title>
            <link>https://chris7462.github.io/music/2024/11/24/about</link>
            <guid>https://chris7462.github.io/music/2024/11/24/about</guid>
            <pubDate>Sun, 24 Nov 2024 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
            <description><![CDATA[Playing the piano has been a childhood dream of mine — something I always wanted to do but never had the chance to pursue. In November 2024, I finally decided to make it happen.]]></description>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Playing the piano has been a childhood dream of mine — something I always wanted to do but never had the chance to pursue. In November 2024, I finally decided to make it happen.</p>
<!-- -->
<p>I am entirely self-taught. Most of my learning comes from watching YouTube videos, studying how others play, and learning by ear. I'm still working on reading sheet music, so a lot of what I play is learned by observation and repetition rather than from notation.</p>
<p>This section of the site is where I share pieces I've been working on. They are not perfect, and that's okay — this is a journal of progress, not a recital.</p>]]></content:encoded>
